imdb.plot outline: Seabass the Rottweiler is a hero in his own mind. He takes on the establishment by robbing the corrupt puppet, Sheriff Joey, and giving the money back to the orphan children. The turmoil develops into a cataclysmic rivalry. The Sheriff repeatedly attempts to antagonize Seabass, but his plans are foiled as he is always outsmarted by the noble canine.
imdb.title: Seabass: The Bandit of Justice
akas: Seabass: The Bandit of Justice (United States)
